# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ── EXPLICITLY TRACKED ──
# The models/ directory and its .pkl binaries are intentionally
# version-controlled so the app boots without a training step.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
!models/
!models/*.pkl
!Dataset/
!Dataset/*.csv
